{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a198ec3a-1656-47c7-bf6b-17bd9699eb6d","content":"No files found in the working directory. Since there's no existing file, here's exactly what you need to do:\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` root element, pointing at your ViewModel:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n\n        <Picker Title=\"Theme\"\n                SelectedItem=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n\n        <HorizontalStackLayout Spacing=\"10\">\n            <Label Text=\"Notifications\" VerticalOptions=\"Center\" />\n            <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        </HorizontalStackLayout>\n\n        <HorizontalStackLayout Spacing=\"10\">\n            <Label Text=\"Font Size\" VerticalOptions=\"Center\" />\n            <Stepper Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\"\n                     Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"36\" Increment=\"1\" />\n            <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='{0}pt'}\" />\n        </HorizontalStackLayout>\n\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n**Key change:** the single addition of `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` converts every `{Binding}` in the page into a compiled binding. The XAML compiler resolves property names at build time instead of using reflection at runtime.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\nCompiled bindings already emit **build errors** if you typo a property name (e.g., `{Binding Themee}` → `XC0045: Binding: Property \"Themee\" not found`).\n\nTo enforce this project-wide so no one can accidentally use uncompiled bindings, add this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <!-- Warn on any binding without x:DataType -->\n  <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### Quick summary\n\n| What | How |\n|---|---|\n| Enable compiled bindings | Add `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` on the root element |\n| Scope to a subtree | Put `x:DataType` on any element; children inherit it |\n| Opt out locally | Use `x:DataType=\"x:Null\"` on a subtree that needs reflection bindings |\n| Catch errors at build | Misspelled properties become **compiler errors** automatically |\n| Enforce project-wide | Set `MauiStrictXamlCompilation` in `.csproj` |","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"635ede7b-4eb5-4442-932b-90667b201476","outputTokens":711,"requestId":"DBC5:127F79:83C3D:A6D0B:69F54A3A"},"id":"70673431-4853-4508-afe6-089212b72106","timestamp":"2026-05-02T00:50:18.231Z","parentId":"d0b11272-2ef1-497b-9d36-8af04e264cfc"}
